# tack.tape — kernel as language. Tack expression resolves to a verb.
# Pre: cd into any ostk-init'd dir.

Output "/Users/scottmeyer/projects/ostk-site/v2/public/assets/demo/tack.gif"
Output "/Users/scottmeyer/projects/ostk-site/v2/public/assets/demo/tack.mp4"

Set FontFamily "Monaco"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1100
Set Height 320
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 60ms

Sleep 400ms

Type `ostk tack ':needle 1' --json`
Enter
Sleep 2500ms
